title: Ep. 651 - AOC Attends The Jussie Smollett School Of Victimology
description:
Today on the Matt Walsh Show, did AOC attend the Jussie Smollett school of victimology? New revelations cast doubt on her claims of a near death experience during the January 6 riot. Also Five Headlines including John Kerry explaining why he has to travel by private jet to save the planet, and the news media is horrified and scandalized by a grocery store in Florida where people aren’t wearing a mask. And in our Daily Cancellation we will contend with the ACLU’s attempt to “debunk” biological science. Is biology canceled, or the ACLU?
